data.description:
Greentech Technology International Limited ( (HK:0195) ) just unveiled an update.

Greentech Technology International Limited has appointed OCF Corporate Advisory Limited as an internal control consultant to conduct an independent review of its internal controls, a necessary step for the resumption of trading in the company’s shares. data.title: Shanghai Realway Capital’s Subsidiary Enters Consulting Agreement with Xinhe Credit
data.description:

This agreement involves Yuanhui Qichuang providing consulting management services for Xinhe Credit’s distressed personal loan assets, including strategy formulation, inventory checks, and legal consultations. The transaction is considered a continuing connected transaction under Hong Kong’s Listing Rules, requiring annual review and reporting but exempt from shareholder approval.
